oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Cedar Hill & Company Orchard Company receipt, Winchester, Tennessee, circa 1900
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: A receipt circa 1900 issued to John Sadler of Hughes, Tennessee for part payment for a bill of nursery stock from the Cedar Hill & Company Orchard Company, Winchester, Tennessee. It is signed by J.W. Shadow, Manager and A.A. Byrnes, Salesman. Forms part of the Arcade Music Collection. 1 document.
